Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:27.29,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So heavy, dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:50.61,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:53.44,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.40,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}Breaking news, dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:58.28,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}A serial shooting has occurred this afternoon in Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:03.52,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}Of the two victims, one has passed away, and the other is in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.38,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}The deceased's identity is currently unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:09.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}The boy in critical condition is Jinnai Enta-kun, 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.17,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey, it's Specs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.21,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}How come you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:21.80,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He helped me out with some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.93,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Was he your buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:33.60,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}Wanted fugitive Kuji Chikai is suspected of having been involved with the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:33.60,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Come on. Not everything is my fault, damn it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:38.11,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You can go back if you want, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.18,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}If you want out, it's now or never.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.24,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You can't go back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.50,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}Runaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.99,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Asakusa Sara TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He has someone who's closer to him than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:56.13,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But I'm the only one who can be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.63,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The bad ones are the ones to survive in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:03.15,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Specs was a good person. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.35,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Please, Yasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:11.39,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It was a pair of cops who shot Enta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.92,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Enta protected me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.83,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Calm down, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.40,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The shooter was Kuji Chikai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.78,1080P思源英文标准位置,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We lifted Kuji's fingerprints off the candies Enta-kun had.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.28,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.25,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I saw it with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.53,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The cops...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.29,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's okay now, Kazu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.35,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.52,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.15,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You must have been scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:40.30,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Thanks for helping Enta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.30,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's my fault this happened to Enta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.21,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're not at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.80,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Whoever shot Enta is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:50.48,1080P思源英文标准位置,Nurse,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Jinnai-san, this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.22,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why won't anyone believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:03.07,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Someone, please, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.88,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Toi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.83,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.96,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I told you to lay low, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.38,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.93,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You were late, so I got worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.33,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This is my kid brother, Toi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:25.57,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And this is Masa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:26.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm Masa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.63,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I've been given the honor of taking care of your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.12,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Nice to meet you, Toi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.47,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Who's taking care of {\i1}who{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.72,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ow, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Seriously, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}A middle school kid making bank on weed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.10,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I can totally believe he's your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:41.48,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I want some of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:45.29,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}As you can see, he's a moron,but he's my little bro from the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.45,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're about the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:47.15,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You'll get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.66,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Mabu... Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.16,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Are you {\i1}my{\i0} Mabu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.50,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.34,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He's the real Mabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.80,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:13.68,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I finally have you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Otters...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Soiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:29.32,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm not going to mess this up, dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.07,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:31.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:32.97,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.05,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.25,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This is the last piece, dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.29,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Let's forced defrosting, dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.91,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.26,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm glad you're safe, dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.70,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I thought I was dead, kero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.11,1080P思源英文标准位置,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're beautiful no matter how you look, dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.87,1080P思源英文标准位置,Shop,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Have a free candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.49,1080P思源英文标准位置,Shop,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:14.99,1080P思源英文标准位置,Shop,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:21.66,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Your brother has some real balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.53,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:26.21,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He's not like your average brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:31.01,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I mean, he took out the head of Yurikamome when he was ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:34.51,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I told you, I was the one who killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.06,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:39.49,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You brought the Kamome boss's balls to our pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.14,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And that's how you came to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.40,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Lucky for you that your brother did that for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.89,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Shut the hell up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.02,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:50.15,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I only said what's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.91,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They said Enta might not make it through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.51,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:09.30,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kazu-kun, would you stay by his side and speak to him for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.39,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.90,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I don't have the right to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.73,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:20.54,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He's indebted to you, and you're dear to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:25.44,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The people in our family get assigned to work overseas a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:28.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It was four years ago that Enta and I came back to Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:33.86,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He had a hard time fitting in with his classmates, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.57,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:42.57,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:45.08,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Want to pass the ball to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.97,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:52.21,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You always watch us play soccer here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:56.79,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'll end up making you an outcast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.85,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You should pretend you have no business with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.47,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I totally have business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.48,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I want to play soccer with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The two of us can totally become a golden duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:14.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm Jinnai Enta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm Yasaka Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.91,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.73,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.71,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He was really happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.74,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Enta told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.67,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}"I'm never going to let Kazuki become lonely."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:35.70,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}"I'm always going to be by his side, no matter what."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:37.01,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.78,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.59,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You go on and on about shit that doesn't matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:51.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}yet you get yourself hurt without telling me what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.11,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:57.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Smile like you always do, Enta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:58.95,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:09:59.95,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.73,1080P思源英文标准位置,Voice,0,0,0,,{\blur4\a6}Kappa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:02.01,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}En—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.13,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:04.87,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}My sister and the others will notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.06,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Enta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:08.71,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:12.47,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I gobbled him up and turned him into a kappa, kero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.57,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Keppi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.90,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Where've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.23,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's a long story, kero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:18.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:19.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.49,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It sounds like a time bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:26.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's a timer that indicates how much longer Enta has to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.02,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.24,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I can't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.71,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Calm down, Enta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.18,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:35.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'll save you, Enta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:38.37,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We'll get the dishes of Hope back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:39.95,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:44.86,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But I ended up this way because I deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.89,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Like, it's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's totally my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.77,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We're the golden duo, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.34,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}K-Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.08,1080P思源英文标准位置,Enta,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kazuki! Kazuki, Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:02.97,1080P思源英文标准位置,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now that that's settled, we shall fight the decisive battle tonight, kero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:10.95,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Use this ticket to get to the island, and then transfer to another boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.23,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.74,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:16.98,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Please take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:19.58,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm glad I got to meet you, too, Toi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.50,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:30.12,1080P思源英文标准位置,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:31.88,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.13,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The ship's leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.40,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.28,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why do you have a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:41.79,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why did you shoot him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:45.00,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Masa wouldn't have survived in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.13,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why I did him the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.39,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.89,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:55.31,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Damn it, now I have to deal with this asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:59.15,1080P思源英文标准位置,Taka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bro, I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.56,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Taka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.18,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}How did you know to find me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:06.63,1080P思源英文标准位置,Taka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's easy to find information about someone with as many enemies as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.38,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Wow, that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:11.16,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}After how much I took care of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.18,1080P思源英文标准位置,Taka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You shot Masa with that gun, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:17.83,1080P思源英文标准位置,Taka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Killing your own people just to protect yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.42,1080P思源英文标准位置,Taka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That does sound like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:23.34,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I make a point of using up my bullets early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:28.35,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Otherwise, traitorous shitheads like you start popping up everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:34.37,1080P思源英文标准位置,Taka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This is the last time we'll hear your big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.57,1080P思源英文标准位置,Taka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You'll get killed by us or the fuzz'll catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.61,1080P思源英文标准位置,Taka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Either way, all that awaits you is hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.51,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:52.58,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm going to kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.34,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.10,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}D-Dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.10,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:20.27,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The two of us are a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.11,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The ultimate couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.75,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey, sorry I'm back so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:30.61,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I brought home some of your favorite pancakes, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.98,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Otter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Otter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.38,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Mabu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.62,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You look like you're in otter agony, Mabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.73,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.22,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Please don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.88,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Please watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.99,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Otter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.89,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.61,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What are those two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.40,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Get away from Mabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.90,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Reo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:10.49,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What the hell do you think you're doing to Mabu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:13.91,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.62,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Otter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.53,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I am an otter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.67,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But I'm also you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.42,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:25.95,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We otters exist in this world as concepts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:30.05,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I am a mirror of the desires inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.81,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:36.31,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're the one who wants to own Mabu, Reo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:41.19,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You wanted to lock lips with this hollow machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.56,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:48.19,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're merely being made to dance by your desires—by us otters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:52.20,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now, Mabu, what matters the most to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.70,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.66,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Or me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.71,1080P思源英文标准位置,Otter,0,0,0,,{\blur4}How do I look to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:04.71,1080P思源英文标准位置,Reo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Right now, I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.38,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I knew you were an imposter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:14.10,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I was an idiot for believing you, even for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:18.58,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm going to take back the real Mabu with my own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.09,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Just one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:24.48,1080P思源英文标准位置,Mabu,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I just need one more dish of Hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.61,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kazu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.24,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sorry, did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.24,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Are you going somewhere, Kazu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.79,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:40.50,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.25,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Are you leaving without telling me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.26,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm not that clueless anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:50.07,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:52.97,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm about to go help Enta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Is it dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.33,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.62,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.39,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This time, it's my turn to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:07.48,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Enta-niichan always helped me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:10.90,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He was with me every week during rehab, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:15.28,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I guess a lot happened that I didn't know about, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:20.66,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Enta-niichan and I had the same wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:31.25,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Isn't that awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.27,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Is this me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:37.39,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're going to run again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:43.27,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You used to like this player before, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.41,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's right, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:57.32,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I love it when you're running.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.11,1080P思源英文标准位置,Haruka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.34,1080P思源英文标准位置,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.96,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You only live once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.11,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You don't get extra lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.47,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}When things aren't working out, just throw it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:17.89,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.73,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yo, I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.82,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:26.96,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.36,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why do you have that gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:34.36,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I swapped it out before you threw it out four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.45,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.12,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's my kid brother for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:45.33,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Are you going to throw me, your kid brother, out, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:49.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I don't care if you're a bad person to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.96,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're my brother, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.72,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You're a little too good to be my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:05.23,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The bad ones are the ones who survive in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.42,1080P思源英文标准位置,Taka,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.67,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.68,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.19,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You need to get to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.19,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.69,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.22,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:39.58,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I had everything planned to work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:40.96,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Stop talking already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:44.47,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You ruined everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.97,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:46.96,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:50.49,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Keep yourself fed with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:54.71,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Son of a bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:21:02.74,1080P思源英文标准位置,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's such a pain in the ass,trying to connect...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:42.85,1080P思源英文标准位置,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Fuck!
Comment: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:27.29,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}中文对话字幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:27.29,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太重了 dish……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:50.61,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Keppi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:53.44,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.40,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}紧急新闻 dish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:58.28,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}今天下午浅草地区发生了连环枪击案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:03.52,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}两起案件的受害者 一个已经死亡了 另一个意识不清的状态中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.38,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}死者的身份暂时无法确认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:09.41,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}处在重伤状态的受害者是14岁的男孩阵内燕太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.17,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嘿 这不是那位老哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.21,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哥哥你怎么知道他的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:21.80,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他帮了我忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.93,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他是你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:33.60,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}通缉中的逃犯久慈誓被怀疑和案件有关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:33.60,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不可能所有的事儿都怪到我头上嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:38.11,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果你想回就回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.18,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就现在你还有得选了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.24,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}过会你就回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.50,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\a6}快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.99,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Sara,0,0,0,,{\blur4}浅草皿电视台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.82,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他有更亲近的人惦记着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:56.13,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但只有我能站在哥哥身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.63,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个世界只有坏人才能生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:03.15,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Toi,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那家伙是个好人 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.35,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜托你了 矢逆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:11.39,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是两个警察枪击的燕太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.92,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}燕太保护了我……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.83,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小伙子你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.40,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}杀手是久慈誓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.78,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Cop 1,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们从燕太的糖果上找到了久慈的指纹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.28,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.25,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我亲眼所见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.53,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那些警察……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.29,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没事啦 一稀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.35,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}老师 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.52,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.15,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你肯定是特别害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:40.30,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你帮助了燕太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.30,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}燕太的事是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.21,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.80,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}错在枪击了燕太的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:50.48,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Nurse,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阵内 这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.81,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Otone,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.22,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么没人愿意相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:03.07,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.88,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Kazuki,0,0,0,,{\blur4}悠……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.83,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.96,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}混蛋 我跟你说了要低调点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.38,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.93,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你迟到了 所以我很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.33,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是我弟弟悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:25.57,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个是雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:26.59,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.63,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很荣幸能照看大哥你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.12,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请多指教 悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.47,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Chikai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是谁照看{\i1}谁{\i0} 啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.72,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有点疼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.81,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.81,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}中学生通过{\s1}烟草{\s0}来赚钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.10,1080P思源黑体中等字幕,Masa,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不愧是大哥你的亲弟弟啊
